We record it in the protocol.

01:19:40.500 --> 01:19:45.000
After a while, the name of what we see, just some vague concepts,

01:19:45.000 --> 01:19:47.500
ideas will begin to appear.

01:19:48.000 --> 01:19:49.500
Real ideas.

01:19:50.000 --> 01:19:51.500
We continue to record them.

01:19:52.000 --> 01:19:53.500
At first, the ideas are empty.

